      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. This car has been my total pride and joy, and honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been incredibly well-loved and babied since day one\u2014always kept in the garage and maintained to perfection. If you're looking for a ride that's in truly pristine condition and ready for some new adventures, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to a great new home!",
