      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade specimen that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, and its condition is nothing short of breathtaking. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings, thanks to a multi-stage paint correction and a professional ceramic coating. Every body panel is original with factory-perfect gaps. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather seats are supple and show zero bolster wear or creasing, while the carpets have been protected by original floor mats since day one. All electronics, from the infotainment system to the smallest ambient light, function exactly as they did on the showroom floor. Mechanically, this car is flawless. It has a comprehensive, documented service history with every maintenance interval performed ahead of schedule at the authorized dealership. The engine bay is detailed and dry, the transmission shifts are imperceptibly smooth, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. This sale includes all original keys, the complete owner\u2019s manual set, and a folder of every service receipt. For the buyer who demands perfection without compromise, this is the one.",
